{
  "chapter": 3,
  "chapter_summary": "第三回 天池府\n\n芮玮冒充简召舞进入天池府，由丫环春琴、夏诗、秋书、冬画带路前往简老夫人居所万寿居。途中听到一缕悲凄箫音，得知是简召舞未婚妻刘育芷所吹。丫环们注意到\"公子\"性情大变，秋书甚至怀疑他不是本人。\n\n芮玮在万寿居见到简怀萱（简召舞之妹），以生病为由解释自己的变化。随后拜见简老夫人，见到简召稽（简召舞之弟，性格懦弱惧兄）。简老夫人告知山西黑堡来信威胁，要取回简公在世时搜夺的财物，命芮玮以武功应对。\n\n芮玮离开万寿居后，简怀萱追来邀请他明日去后山猎狮，芮玮无法拒绝，心中暗自叫苦。本章展现了芮玮在天池府中的伪装困境，以及简家内部的人物关系和潜在危机。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_chun_qin",
      "speaker_name": "春琴",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "公子可要去见刘小姐？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "刘小姐？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_shi",
      "speaker_name": "夏诗",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "自公子去后，半年来刘小姐无一日不在此时独自弄箫，公子最好先去见见她！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不用！不用！",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chun_qin",
      "speaker_name": "春琴",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "公子，奴婢们在此等候！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "等什么！一起上去吧！",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_shi",
      "speaker_name": "夏诗",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "公子！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chun_qin",
      "speaker_name": "春琴",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "公子不知老夫人一向不许奴婢们上万寿居吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我糊涂了！你们也不用在此等候，等会我自己回书房，你们去吧！",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wei_ya_huan",
      "speaker_name": "六位丫环",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "主母等候大公子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_hua",
      "speaker_name": "冬画",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "奇怪啊！半年不见公子好像变了一个人？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qiu_shu",
      "speaker_name": "秋书",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不对！不对！他好像不是大公子？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_shi",
      "speaker_name": "夏诗",
      "listener": "char_qiu_shu",
      "text": "你乱说什么！公子不过性情改变，岂可瞎想！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chun_qin",
      "speaker_name": "春琴",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一个人的性情不能变得那么快呀？公子以前的性情完全不是这样和善的呀？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_shi",
      "speaker_name": "夏诗",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我看公子没什么改变他的性情，他不是不去见刘小姐吗？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_hua",
      "speaker_name": "冬画",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们的公子也真太无情了！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chun_qin",
      "speaker_name": "春琴",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不要说啦，我们回去吧！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "简怀萱",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "大哥！大哥！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "text": "妹妹！",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "简怀萱",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你……你……怎么瘦了？而且……声音也变了？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "text": "哦！是吗？这半年来大哥害了一场大病，嗓子都变得沙哑了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 117
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "简怀萱",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "生了什么病呀？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "text": "也没有什么！只是遭了风寒，妈好吗？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "简怀萱",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "妈的身体安健。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_jian_lao_fu_ren",
      "text": "孩儿叩见母亲！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "简老夫人",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "起来！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhao_ji",
      "speaker_name": "简召稽",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "大……大……哥好……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_jian_zhao_ji",
      "text": "弟弟近来可好？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhao_ji",
      "speaker_name": "简召稽",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "好……好……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "简老夫人",
      "listener": "char_jian_zhao_ji",
      "text": "讲话怎么老发抖呀？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_zhao_ji",
      "speaker_name": "简召稽",
      "listener": "char_jian_lao_fu_ren",
      "text": "妈，我……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "简老夫人",
      "listener": "char_jian_zhao_ji",
      "text": "好，你出去，妈和你大哥说几句话。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "简老夫人",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "半年来在外做了何事？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_jian_lao_fu_ren",
      "text": "半年来浪迹江湖，孩儿生了一场病，弄得一事无成！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "简老夫人",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "既生病为何不回来休养？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_jian_lao_fu_ren",
      "text": "孩儿病重，无法回转。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "简老夫人",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "自你父亲去世，当朝失了权势，江湖人物以为简家从此衰败，倒觊觎起天池府的宝物啦！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_jian_lao_fu_ren",
      "text": "谁有这种企图？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "简老夫人",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "半月前金陵第一镖局总镖头送来一函，说是从山西带来的，你拿去看！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_jian_lao_fu_ren",
      "text": "天池府不可受此轻辱，当要阻止他们的强梁行为！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "简老夫人",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "当然要阻止，这件事不能报官，只有靠自己的力量，简家数你武功最高，你既回来，一切由你看着办吧！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_jian_lao_fu_ren",
      "text": "是的，母亲！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "简老夫人",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "没有别的事了，出去吧！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "简怀萱",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "大哥！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "简怀萱",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "大哥，明天我们去猎狮吧！",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "text": "你说什么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "简怀萱",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "去捉狮子！",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "text": "捉狮子？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "简怀萱",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "大哥不是喜欢捉狮子玩吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "text": "唔！唔！",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "简怀萱",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "那就好啦！明天早上我们到后山去，好久没有玩狮子了。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "text": "这么晚了快进去吧！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "简怀萱",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "明天一定要去玩狮子噢？",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "text": "那不成！",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "简怀萱",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "一定要去，我明天早上预备好用具，来拖大哥去。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 252
    }
